_sText:
Little FY map where you slide down to the arena. You have a choice between 2 slides. One is faster, but more dangerous...

Features:
-Barrel Slide (dangerous)
-Sled Slide (slow & safe)
-Symetrical Arena with props, towers, walls, more.

Install:
Save the .bsp to your C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\[name]\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps.
NO .NAV FILE, ITS NOT NEEDED TO PLAY.

Author: GabrielPapaK

Time: 2hours.

Hope you enjoy!
